<Body>
    <Title>八达岭高速因多车追尾3人死亡封闭7小时</Title>
    <ReportTime type="absTime">2008-04-15</ReportTime>
    <Content>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent">
                    <Participant sid="s1">本报</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter>
                </Event>（实习生 彭科峰 吴旖旎 记者 任冠军）
                <Event eid="e2">
                    <Time tid="t2" type="relTime">昨天凌晨4点半左右</Time>，
                    <Location lid="l2">八达岭高速出京方向距康庄收费站1.5公里处</Location>，
                    <Object sid="s2">5辆大货车</Object>发生
                    <Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">追尾</Denoter>
                </Event>，致
                <Event eid="e3">
                    <Participant sid="s3">3人</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter>
                </Event>
                <Event eid="e4">
                    <Participant sid="s4">2人</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e5">受
                    <Object oid="o5">事故</Object>
                    <Denoter type="perception" did="d5">影响</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e6">
                    <Location lid="l6">该路段</Location>
                    <Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">封闭</Denoter>
                    <Time tid="t6" type="timeInterval">7个多小时</Time>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e7" type="thoughtevent">
                    <Participant sid="s7">目击者周立军</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d7" type="statement">说</Denoter>
                </Event>，当时天色比较暗，高速路上由西向东行驶的汽车车速都很快。
            </Sentence>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e8">
                    <Denoter type="movement" did="d8">临近</Denoter>
                    <Location lid="l8">康庄收费站</Location>时
                </Event>,
                <Event eid="e9">
                    <Object sid="s9,s8,s10">一辆大货车</Object>突然
                    <Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">减速</Denoter>
                </Event>
                <Event eid="e10">
                    <Denoter did="d10" type="action">刹车</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e11">
                    <Object sid="s11">其后的多辆货车</Object>也相继
                    <Denoter did="d11" type="action">刹车</Denoter>
                </Event>，造成
                <Event eid="e12">
                    <Object sid="s12">5车</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d12" type="emergency">追尾</Denoter>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e13">
                    <Denoter did="d13" type="emergency">事</Denoter>发
                </Event>后，
                <Event eid="e14">
                    <Object sid="s14">汽车零件</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d14" type="action">散落一地</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e15">
                    <Object sid="s15,s16">第三辆追尾货车</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d15" type="action">横</Denoter>在
                    <Location lid="l15">马路中间</Location>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e16">且有
                    <Denoter did="d16" type="action">漏油</Denoter>现象
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e17">
                    <Object sid="s17">一辆拉钢管的大货车</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d17" type="stateChange">受损</Denoter>严重
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e18">
                    <Object oid="o18">整个驾驶室</Object>被
                    <Denoter did="d18" type="stateChange">撞瘪</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e19">
                    <Participant oid="o19" sid="s20">驾驶室内的3名男子</Participant>被
                    <Denoter did="d19" type="action">夹</Denoter>在
                    <Location lid="l19">中间</Location>
                </Event>
                <Event polarity="negative" eid="e20">无法
                    <Denoter did="d20" type="action">动弹</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e21">
                    <Object sid="s21">车上所载的大量钢管</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d21" type="action">掉落</Denoter>
                    <Location lid="l21">地面</Location>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e22">
                    <Object sid="s22">其他车辆</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d22" type="stateChange">受损</Denoter>均不严重
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
        </Paragraph>
